</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>中國製山寨 PS5 外國網上熱賣，外型極似 PS5 + 售價 HK$180</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/11/30/ps5-gs5/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=ps5-gs5</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Christy]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 30 Nov 2021 07:50:52 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[AliExpress]]></category><category><![CDATA[Game Satation 5]]></category><category><![CDATA[PS5]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1073542</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>PS5 自推出後便造成搶購潮，更因全球晶片缺貨而缺貨，長期供不應求。有中國網上平台近期卻出現一台酷似 PS5  [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>PS5 自推出後便造成搶購潮，更因全球晶片缺貨而缺貨，長期供不應求。有中國網上平台近期卻出現一台酷似 PS5 的遊戲機，以約 180 元港幣出售。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-6.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1073550" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-6-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-6-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-6-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-6-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-6-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-6.jpg 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-5.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1073551" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-5-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-5-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-5-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-5-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-5-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-5.jpg 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-7-scaled-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1073557" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-7-scaled-1-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-7-scaled-1-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-7-scaled-1-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-7-scaled-1-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-7-scaled-1-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-7-scaled-1-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-7-scaled-1-2048x2048.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-7-scaled-1.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p><p>這部與 PS5 外型幾乎一樣的遊戲機名為 Game Station 5，於阿里巴巴旗下的國際電商平台 AliExpress 出售。與 PS5 有別的是，Game Station 5 配備有線控制器，而且只能運行 FC 遊戲。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-3.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1073552" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-3-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-3-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-3-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-3-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-3-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-3.jpg 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1073553" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-2-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-2-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-2-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-2-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-2-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-2.jpg 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-4.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1073554" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-4-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-4-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-4-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-4-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-4-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/GS5-4.jpg 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p><p>有很多買家在平台上都給予這部 Game Station 5 好評，有來自西班牙的買家將 Game Station 5 送給兒子作生日禮物，並對此十分滿意。更有網民指 Game Station 5 是唯一支援 16k 解像度的設備，笑稱絕不能輕看。</p><p>資料來源： <a href="https://pcucgame.com/ps5-gamestation-5/">蝦米攻略網</a></p><p>—</p><p><u>unwire.hk </u>Mewe 專頁 : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><u>https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</u></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
